{"word":"G4820 - συμβάλλω - symbállō - soom-bal'-lo - Confer","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συμβάλλω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">symbállō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">soom-bal'-lo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Confer</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சிந்தனை பண்ணு, சந்தி, யோசனைபண்ணு"},{"paragraph":"to throw together, to bring together, to converse"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4862 - σύν - sýn - soon/4862\">G4862</a> and <a href=\"#/G906 - βάλλω - bállō - bal'-lo/906\">G906</a>; to <i>combine</i>, that is, (in speaking) to <i>converse</i>, <i>consult</i>, <i>dispute</i>, (mentally) to <i>consider</i>, (by implication) to <i>aid</i>, (personally) to <i>join</i>, <i>attack:</i> - confer, encounter, help, make, meet with, ponder.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}